klang/issues/1/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hzdgopher/4klang/issues/1/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hzdgopher/4klang/issues/1/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/hzdgopher/4klang/pull/1", "id": 386572008, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MjM1MjY2OTI4", "number": 1, "title": "Mac OSX player and Single tick rendering", "user": {"login": "petersalomonsen", "id": 9760441, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjk3NjA0NDE=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9760441?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen", "html_url": "https://github.com/petersalomonsen", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/petersalomonsen/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2018-12-02T15:51:53Z", "updated_at": "2019-08-17T18:17:57Z", "closed_at": "2019-08-17T18:17:57Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "draft": false, "pull_request": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hzdgopher/4klang/pulls/1", "html_url": "https://github.com/hzdgopher/4klang/pull/1", "diff_url": "https://github.com/hzdgopher/4klang/pull/1.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/hzdgopher/4klang/pull/1.patch", "merged_at": "2019-08-17T18:17:57Z"}, "body": "- Use AUTHORING mode for rendering one tick per invocation of _4klang_render\r\n- Example for running player on Mac OSX\r\n\r\nI'm not sure about the purpose of the AUTHORING flag, but I noticed that it stores the current tick - so I assumed that it would be useful to use that stored value when `_4klang_render` is invoked the next time. Also then it made more sense to just render 1 tick instead of the whole song.\r\n\r\nIf I've misunderstood the purpose of the AUTHORING flag, I can create a new flag instead for adding the feature of rendering a single tick. Rendering of single ticks is useful for having control of the song position, and also to get instant audio output without having to wait for the whole song to be rendered.", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hzdgopher/4klang/issues/1/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hzdgopher/4klang/issues/1/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null, "score": 1.0}]}